= photo(:src => cdn_url('asia2017/day-two/_DSC0235.jpg'), :ratio => 1.506, :class => "full")
%p At the end of the trail we were rewarded with a beautiful beach to cool off.

= photo(:src => cdn_url('asia2017/day-two/_DSC0239.jpg'), :ratio => 1.506)

%p Most people took a taxi or shuttle-bus back, but we backtracked the last part of the trail to head to the nearest subway station. It took us across a very large cemetery.

